=== Intransitive verb ===

'''to freeze''' ([[froze]], [[frozen]])

# to be very [[cold]] (a [[temperature]] below 0 [[degree]]s [[celsius]])
# to [[become]] [[hard]] [[due]] to [[low]] [[temperature]] (for [[liquid]]s)
# to become [[motionless]].  (''The squirrel froze when it saw the hawk overhead.'')

